<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَمَنْ لَمْ يَقْدِرْ عَلَى وَفَاءِ شَيْءٍ مِنْ دَيْنِهِ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ هُوَ مُؤَجَّلٌ:</span> تَحْرُمُ مُطَالَبَتُهُ، وَحَبْسُهُ، وَكَذَا مُلَازَمَتُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا يَحِلُّ مُؤَجَّلٌ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- بِفَلَسٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا بِمَوْتٍ إِنْ وَثَّقَ الوَرَثَةُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> بِرَهْنٍ مُحْرِزٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> أَوْ كَفِيلٍ مَلِيءٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ ظَهَرَ غَرِيمٌ بَعْدَ القِسْمَةِ:</span> رَجَعَ عَلَى الغُرَمَاءِ بِقِسْطِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَيُحْجَرُ عَلَى الصَّغِيرِ، وَالمَجْنُونِ،<span class="c5"> وَالسَّفِيهِ:</span> لِحَظِّهِمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ دَفَعَ إِلَيْهِمْ مَالَهُ بِعَقْدٍ أَوْ لَا:</span> رَجَعَ فِيمَا بَقِيَ، لَا مَا تَلِفَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَضْمَنُونَ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- جِنَايَةً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَإِتْلَافَ مَا لَمْ يُدْفَعْ إِلَيْهِمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>